version_description:
-Optimized plugins’ General Settings page;
-You can now move devices among different homes through long tapping the ‘move’ icon;
-Optimized UI design.

-Adjustments in homepage grid view;
-You can now have 10 automations;
-Optimized firmware update;

-New features in Profile;
-You can share photos with the printer (Mainland China only);
-You can view devices' battery information in Consumables (Mainland China only); 
-Optimized notifications for device sharing;
-Optimized display format of offline device plugins;
-Optimized timing function

-Optimized homepage environment info;
-You can now turn on/off push notification for each device;
-Optimized paring process for Bluetooth devices.

-Xiao Ai Voice Settings available in Lab Features (Mainland China only);
-New dynamic effects available on homepage background;
-You can now delete the shared device history;
-You can now share to WhatsApp (exclusing Mainland China);
-Optimized sign-in/sign-up functions;
-Fixed bugs that occur when initializing ZigBee devices；
-Bug fixed.

-Updated home page;
-Optimized names of category navigation;
-Status of consumables now available in “Profile” (now supports air purifier and water purifier, available in Mainland China only);
-Server list is now shown by countries;
-Third-party device page available in “Profile” (Mainland China only);
-Optimized general timing module; 
-Optimized loading speed of plugins;
-Optimized pairing procedure for Bluetooth security chip products (Mainland China only);
-List mode is no longer available;
-Bug fixes.

-Voice service now supports multiple languages;
-Fixed several issues with cameras;
-Optimized photo printing function;
-Optimized functions of Smartmi heater.

-Now supports Mesh devices;
-Optimized loading speed of main page;
-Optimized payment of camera cloud storage;
-Camera’s Cloud storage service supports in-app payment
-Mi Home Smart Lock now supports passcode changing;
-Bug fixes.

Latest updates:
-New status bar to display dynamic information of your home;
-Display devices by type to better search and use them;
-No more "Frequently Used", and you can see all your devices in "My Device"; -Select to display devices by grid or by list;
-Customize device shortcut cards;
-Optimized UI display of device cards.

New features：
