New features：
-Supports new devices;
-App now supports Polish;
-App now supports Vietnamese;
Optimization：
-You can now create up to 128 scenes;
-Optimized redirection to H5;

New features:
-Now supporting Japanese and Thai;

Optimized:
-Network structural upgrade to improve responding speed of service;
-Status description of bluetooth devices edited.

-Now supports new IKEA devices(available only in Mainland China);
-lumi gateways can now add and control IKEA lights(available only in Mainland China); 
-Optimized the device adding procedure; 
-Siri now in multiple languages; 
-Optimized device cards.

-Now supports Mesh devices;
-Optimized loading speed of main page;
-Optimized payment of camera cloud storage;
-Camera’s Cloud storage service supports in-app payment
-Mi Home Smart Lock now supports passcode changing;
-Bug fixes.

-Voice service now supports multiple languages;
-Fixed several issues with cameras;
-Optimized photo printing function;
-Optimized functions of Smartmi heater.

-Optimized unified structure for plugin;
-Recommended name available for device in the paring process; 
-Optimized widget icon acquisition;
-Optimized scanning page for camera;
-Upgraded UI for camera plugin;
-Safe now supports scanning to add and one-time passcode.

